    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310100/extras/837568073278ee21599ecdd4e042a11a.avif?t=1770962451\" width=1560 height=468 /></span>一款时长不到三小时的短篇故事驱动型视觉小说。无需做出任何选择，您可以放松身心，静静欣赏故事的展开。叙事在不同角色的视角间切换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >愿这个故事能留在您的记忆中，哪怕只是短暂的一瞬。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事梗概</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自从维托尔德被打入医院后，莱诺克斯和达维德便开始互相回避。三年后，莱诺克斯决定主动接近达维德，试图修复他们之间破裂的关系——这令达维德感到无比恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内容警告：屏幕抖动、轻微暴力和酗酒。请玩家谨慎体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过2.2万字，阅读时间约3小时</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化游戏文件，在不影响游戏质量的前提下，文件大小减少了约80%。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310100/extras/b58d784fa4246414694de6843ccb4674.avif?t=1770962451\" width=1560 height=484 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310100/extras/0c78a8329212edd0cc4e4afaa757f44b.avif?t=1770962451\" width=1560 height=490 /></span></p>",
